{"tid":318731,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟而家啲報紙佬識唔識中文","createTime":"2017-07-12T09:54:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-14T05:48:38.000Z","uid":35749,"like":4,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1bd2f2bfa5e0886ffd64ad751ae549393f884bc0","tid":318731,"uid":35749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T09:54:58.000Z","msg":"係咪食白飯食到傻撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/b8eopj4h\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fb8eopj4h&h=7771a482&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9545563b13565da5a3e294c689888c991539fdba","tid":318731,"uid":114097,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T09:56:12.000Z","msg":"馬國明放假一天"},{"pid":"6d86428f13b1c9ee558534ba4730a35a4cbbf00a","tid":318731,"uid":35749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T14:09:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c7ab86ac0ef8ff69a7c3140cc7c8b75dfda22ac","tid":318731,"uid":61744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T14:13:28.000Z","msg":"原意指必須<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c69052464bd44901bed53e467ee63f5268737e3b","tid":318731,"uid":38820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T14:16:16.000Z","msg":"需?"},{"pid":"64b0bfc72bd9adcaf44ff6af6009b463ed5ed90c","tid":318731,"uid":5723,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T14:20:12.000Z","msg":"用在&ldquo;需要&rdquo;後的，必須是名詞；而用在&ldquo;須要&rdquo;後的，必須是動詞。這是語法上的基本法則。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;需要&rdquo;的是物件，或別人的行動；例如：我需要醫生、我需要醫生的醫治、我需要醫生醫治。所以不應該用&ldquo;須&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;須要&rdquo;的是行動，例如：我須要見醫生、我須要接受醫生的醫治。<br />\n<br />\n用&ldquo;需&rdquo;還是&ldquo;須&rdquo;，其實決定於句子要表達的意思。"},{"pid":"82282235df86be02fe1015d592c954db22818463","tid":318731,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T14:22:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用在&ldquo;需要&rdquo;後的，必須是名詞；而用在&ldquo;須要&rdquo;後的，必須是動詞。這是語法上的基本法則。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;需要&rdquo;的是物件，或別人的行動；例如：我需要醫生、我需要醫生的醫治、我需要醫生醫治。所以不應該用&ldquo;須&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;須要&rdquo;的是行動，例如：我須要見醫生、我須要接受醫生的醫治。<br />\n<br />\n用&ldquo;需&rdquo;還是&ldquo;須&rdquo;，其實決定於句子要表達的意思。</blockquote><br />\n你自己作架？華文邊有咁既文法"},{"pid":"359eb4b99f68aeff5ee0b89fde2bdd206e83be1d","tid":318731,"uid":24589,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T14:25:18.000Z","msg":"必須<br />\n○<br />\n「必須」指「一定要」，強調要做甚麼或要怎樣，後面多配動詞或形容詞；「必需」指「應該有」或「必須有」，強調有甚麼事物，後面多配名詞。<br />\n<br />\nFrom 東東<br />\n<br />\n唔覺有咩問題"},{"pid":"48f9defa3d463aa191c1b9df0d3149e9e65d8ab9","tid":318731,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T14:25:49.000Z","msg":"需要同必須既分別係：前者即使想要而要唔到，都唔會有致命影響，後者卻是必不可少，唔要唔得"},{"pid":"6fc025264691e38845473feaf5452748c7a93736","tid":318731,"uid":24589,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T14:27:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>需要同必須既分別係：前者即使想要而要唔到，都唔會有致命影響，後者卻是必不可少，唔要唔得</blockquote><br />\n樓主食白飯食到傻左"},{"pid":"5e8e058aa6725c739722f3b5cadbc9c484bebe5a","tid":318731,"uid":276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T14:27:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>需要同必須既分別係：前者即使想要而要唔到，都唔會有致命影響，後者卻是必不可少，唔要唔得</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁即係而家啲上網佬定報紙佬唔識中文？"},{"pid":"12b73e90fb3a161574e009427c5e9e484147dfa0","tid":318731,"uid":5723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T14:29:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>用在&ldquo;需要&rdquo;後的，必須是名詞；而用在&ldquo;須要&rdquo;後的，必須是動詞。這是語法上的基本法則。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;需要&rdquo;的是物件，或別人的行動；例如：我需要醫生、我需要醫生的醫治、我需要醫生醫治。所以不應該用&ldquo;須&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;須要&rdquo;的是行動，例如：我須要見醫生、我須要接受醫生的醫治。<br />\n<br />\n用&ldquo;需&rdquo;還是&ldquo;須&rdquo;，其實決定於句子要表達的意思。</blockquote><br />\n你自己作架？華文邊有咁既文法</blockquote><br />\n讀多啲書吧清"},{"pid":"7fbb0f07886c002ee52e2541d0e2374fe6c8776e","tid":318731,"uid":18604,"